# Exclude local/dev scripts, but KEEP the build-critical ones: the Docker build runs
# `npm run build` → prebuild → scripts/mirror-ee.js (open-core mirror; no-ops without ee/).
# strip-mirrored-pages.js is kept alongside it for consistency. See docs/OPEN_CORE.md.
